title: Fifty Shades Darker: The Tracklist, and All the Songs We Have So Far
text: Share This Link Copy What’s Your Reaction? Thanks for your reaction Don’t forget to share this with your friends! ← Use Arrows Keys → 1 Fifty Shades Darker: The Tracklist, and All the Songs We Have So Far We're just days away from Fifty Shades Darker , the second installment in the sexy trilogy based on the wildly popular books. While we've gotten plenty of details about the film , the soundtrack is really where it's at. In addition to the hot "Crazy in Love" cover from the trailers and Taylor Swift and Zayn's new joint track , we finally have a full tracklist courtesy of the film's official Twitter. Check out the full list plus the first three songs ahead; the soundtrack will be released on Feb. 10, the same day the movie hits theaters. 42370266,42378704,42379603
